<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Hobby Profile</title>

    <style>

      /* Universal Selector - affects all elements */
      * {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      /* Element Selectors */
      body {
        background-color: beige;
      }

      h1 {
        color: darkred;
      }

      h2 {
        color: teal;
      }

      p {
        color: slategray;
      }

      /* Class Selector */
      .profile-info {
        color: navy;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      /* ID Selector */
      #profile-box {
        background-color: lavender;
      }

    </style>

  </head>
  <body>

    <h1>My Hobby Profile</h1>

    <!-- Inline CSS: Add style="color: ____;" inside this p tag -->
    <p style="color: orange;">Welcome! This page shares a little about me.</p>

    <div id="profile-box">

      <h2>About My Hobbies</h2>
      <p class="profile-info">My name is Alex.</p>
      <p class="profile-info">I enjoy painting landscapes.</p>
      <p class="profile-info">My favourite activity is cycling.</p>
      <p class="profile-info">I love reading adventure books.</p>

    </div>

    <h2>Things I Like</h2>
    <p>My favourite animal is a dolphin.</p>
    <p>My favourite game is badminton.</p>
    <p>My favourite movie is Finding Nemo.</p>

  </body>
</html>
